        <mxCell id="g9V9JZxmERnF9HrKtXqY-43" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;1. LietotДҒjs aizpilda formu pДҒrlЕ«kДҒ вҶ’ nospieЕҫ &quot;Pievienot ierakstu&quot;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;2. script.js ar fetch() nosЕ«ta POST /posts pieprasД«jumu ar JSON datiem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3. server.js saЕҶem pieprasД«jumu un padod to marЕЎrutam routes/posts.js&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. routes/posts.js izsauc validatePost() no utils/, lai pДҒrbaudД«tu datus&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Ja dati derД«gi, izsauc createPost() no db/posts.js&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. createPost() izpilda SQL INSERT uz datubДҒzi&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. Atbilde (jauns ieraksts) tiek nosЕ«tД«ta atpakaДј caur katru slДҒni&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;8. script.js saЕҶem atbildi un atjauno tabulu, parДҒdot paziЕҶojumu&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;9. Ja kДҒdДҒ solД« rodas kДјЕ«da, to pДҒrtver errorHandler.js un ieraksta&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;logs tabulДҒ, un lietotДҒjam tiek parДҒdД«ts paziЕҶojums&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="465" x="-140" y="740" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
